ut significantly\naffecting the accuracy of the original TASK for the bulk 3D materials, when\ncompared to the PBE-GGA and SCAN meta-GGA. We further demonstrate the\napplicability of mTASK by assessing the band structures of TMD nanoribbons with\nrespect to various bending curvatures.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Apr 2021 20:56:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-30"}
