y if the results for several propagation distances are\ncombined, so as to get the dispersion relations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Apr 2021 09:15:39 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Jun 2021 06:19:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-30"}
