k and a lit fiber link, respectively. Moreover,\nrates of 85 and 72 Mb/s are resulting for a trusted receiver scenario. These\nsecure-key rates are well addressing the requirements for time-shared CV-QKD\nsystem in densified 5G radio access networks with cloud-based processing.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 9 Apr 2021 13:44:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-12"}
